              <a href="tel:917976592083" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium leading-6 text-white transition duration-150 ease-in-out bg-black border border-transparent rounded-md hover:bg-gray-800 focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10">
                Call Now
